4671b885-d603-4946-af70-40950d4e5650.Text: Lord Cap'n, there are reports from the enforces of an incursion within the ship by our foes and we have spotted ships of the enemies of humanity at the edge of the system. Which would you prefer to face?

18ed6a24-53ea-4bb7-b1f7-51c36dfcb914.Text: My retinue is restless. I shall take personal command of the crushing of the incursion aboard the ship.

38e0b0cc-45b4-4de0-a964-42dc92c2af28.Text: "Lord Cap'n." {n}Ravor acknowledges you with a nod and turns away.{/n}

414506b3-ae82-4ba7-854d-d270ca79b68b.Text: The crew has become restive. Intercept the voidships of our enemy.
